__e: When he left the bar two men followed him carrying empty whiskey bottles.
And all the empty champagne bottles you can find too.
One of them looked down, and among the empty beer cans... ... and dead barracuda, she saw the long backbone of the great fish... ... that was now just garbage waiting to go out with the tide.
Ruined houses, empty streets, and those who once lived in peace here. Now they have only one goal, and that is to survive at all costs!
